Responsibilities : 
Operate as a technical expert on infrastructure projects pertaining to Okta security and governance, authentication services, directory services, and general IT application design, architecture, capacity planning, operations and DR 
Member of the SSO team 
Maintain documentation on Confluence 
Participate in ongoing technology evaluations and keep up with technology trends and industry standards 
Perform infrastructure service design, implementation, performance analysis, optimization, operations, monitoring, problem resolution, upgrades, process management, and documentation 
Continually analyze and work to improve quality of services offered by Corporate IT 
Ensure new infrastructure technologies are adequately tested and integrated with other Infrastructure and Application Services 
Optimize or re-design existing infrastructure services as needed 
Build and track KPI's to service availability & reliability of infrastructure services 
Suggest improvements based on technology, best practices, or changing requirements 
Articulate and drive roadmaps with Product team for updates on advantages and potential opportunities for new technologies and automation 
Establish close working relationships with Security, Project Management, Product Management, and support teams 
Work with and manage outside consulting technical subject matter experts as needed 
